sql: SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ COMMITTED

SELECT *
FROM `banners`
WHERE (`start_date` <= 1723161600) AND (`end_date` >= 1723247999) AND (`active` = 1)
ORDER BY `start_date`

SELECT 1
FROM `user_logins`
WHERE (`current_auth` IS NOT NULL)
LIMIT 0,1

SELECT *
FROM `roles`
ORDER BY `display_order` ASC, `name` ASC

SELECT *
FROM `fields`
WHERE (`entity_id` = 1)
ORDER BY `is_system` DESC, `location_id` ASC, `display_order`

SELECT *
FROM `fields`
WHERE (`entity_id` = 2)
ORDER BY `is_system` DESC, `location_id` ASC, `display_order`

SELECT `tests`.`id`
FROM `tests`
JOIN `cases` ON cases.id = tests.content_id
WHERE (`run_id` = 13) AND (`is_selected` = 1) AND (((`tests`.`assignedto_id` = 1)))

SELECT `tests`.`id`,`tests`.`status_id`,`tests`.`is_completed`,`tests`.`case_id`,`tests`.`content_id`,`tests`.`added_dynamic`,`cases`.`section_id`,`cases`.`template_id`,`cases`.`title`,`cases`.`priority_id`,`cases`.`refs`,`cases`.`estimate`,`cases`.`type_id`,`cases`.`display_order`,`tests`.`id` AS `tests_id`,`cases`.`title` AS `cases_title`,`tests`.`assignedto_id` AS `tests_assignedto_id`,(SELECT
                    `defects`
                FROM
                    test_changes
                WHERE
                    id = tests.last_status_change_id)
                AS `tests_defects`,`sections`.`name` AS `cases_section_name`
FROM `tests`
JOIN `cases` ON tests.content_id = cases.id
JOIN `sections` ON cases.section_id = sections.id
WHERE (`tests`.`run_id` = 13) AND (`cases`.`is_deleted` = 0) AND (`tests`.`is_selected` = 1) AND (`tests`.`id` IN (2806,2807,2808,2813,2814,2815,2818,2819,2821,2826,2827,2828,2829,2832,2835,2841,2849,2850,2853,2854,2855,2859,2860,2861,2863,2864,2866,2869,2870,2872,2874,2876,2882,2884,2885,2886,2887,2890,2893,2895,2906,2914,2915,2917,2918,2920,2923,2924,2926,2930,2932,2934,2935,2937,2942,2943,2947,2949,2950,2951,2953,2955,2958,2959,2962,2964,2969,2971,2972,2973,2974,2975,2977,2981,2983,2988,2989,2990,2992,2993,2994,2999,3001,3003,3006,3009,3010,3012,3014,3017,3019,3020,3021,3028))
ORDER BY `sections`.`display_order`, `cases`.`display_order`
LIMIT 0,500

SELECT `test_changes`.*
FROM `test_changes`
JOIN `tests` ON test_changes.test_id = tests.id
JOIN `cases` ON tests.content_id = cases.id
JOIN `sections` ON cases.section_id = sections.id
WHERE (`test_changes`.`run_id` = 13) AND (`tests`.`is_selected` = 1)
ORDER BY `sections`.`display_order`, `cases`.`display_order`, `test_changes`.`test_id`, `test_changes`.`id` DESC
